#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:4
msgid "I get some errors related to something called \"FUSE\""
msgstr "我遇到一些與「FUSE」相關的錯誤"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:6
msgid ""
"AppImages require a Linux technology called *Filesystem in Userspace* (or "
"short *FUSE*). The majority of systems ships with a working FUSE setup. "
"However, sometimes, it doesn't quite work. This section explains a few "
"solutions that fix the most frequently reported problems."
msgstr ""
"AppImage 需要一項稱為 *Filesystem in Userspace*（簡稱 *FUSE*）的 Linux 技術。"
"多數系統都預裝可用的 FUSE 設定，但有時仍會無法正常運作。本節說明幾種可修正常"
"見問題的解決方案。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:11
msgid "Contents"
msgstr "目次"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:14
msgid "The AppImage tells me it needs FUSE to run"
msgstr "AppImage 告訴我需要 FUSE 才能執行"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:16
msgid "Sometimes, an AppImage writes the following message to the console:"
msgstr "有時 AppImage 會在主控台輸出下列訊息："

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:19
msgid ""
"AppImages require FUSE to run.\n"
"You might still be able to extract the contents of this AppImage\n"
"if you run it with the --appimage-extract option.\n"
"See https://github.com/AppImage/AppImageKit/wiki/FUSE\n"
"for more information"
msgstr ""
"AppImage 需要 FUSE 才能執行。\n"
"若您以 --appimage-extract 選項執行，\n"
"仍可能可以解壓此 AppImage 的內容。\n"
"請參閱 https://github.com/AppImage/AppImageKit/wiki/FUSE\n"
"以取得更多資訊"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:27
msgid ""
"In this case, FUSE is not properly set up on your system. You will have to :"
"ref:`install FUSE <ref-install-fuse>` in order to fix the problem."
msgstr ""
"此情況表示您的系統上 FUSE 未正確設定。您需要 :ref:`安裝 FUSE <ref-install-"
"fuse>` 才能修正問題。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:30
msgid ""
"When trying to run AppImages which weren't built specifically for your "
"platform, you might see this message as well, even if it doesn't occur while "
"using AppImages built for your platform. Please see :ref:`these instructions "
"<ref-warning-fuse-cross-architecture>` on how to fix the issue."
msgstr ""
"嘗試執行非針對您平台建置的 AppImage 時，即使在執行本平台建置的 AppImage 沒問"
"題，也可能會看到此訊息。請參閱 :ref:`這些指引 <ref-warning-fuse-cross-"
"architecture>` 了解如何修正。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:36
msgid "How to install FUSE"
msgstr "如何安裝 FUSE"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:38
msgid ""
"Most Linux distributions come with a functional FUSE 2.x setup. However, if "
"it is not working for you, you may have to install and configure FUSE 2.y "
"yourself."
msgstr ""
"多數 Linux 散布版預設具備可用的 FUSE 2.x 設定。若無法運作，您可能需要自行安裝"
"並設定 FUSE 2.x。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:40
msgid ""
"The process of installing FUSE highly differs from distribution to "
"distribution. This section shows how to install FUSE on the most common "
"distributions."
msgstr ""
"FUSE 的安裝流程會因散布版而異。本節說明在最常見的散布版上如何安裝 FUSE。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:43
msgid ""
"If your distribution is not listed, please ask the distribution developers "
"for instructions."
msgstr "若您的散布版未列出，請向該散布版的開發者索取指引。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:49
msgid "Setting up FUSE 2.x on Ubuntu (pre-22.04), Debian and their derivatives"
msgstr "在 Ubuntu（22.04 之前）、Debian 及其衍生版本設定 FUSE 2.x"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:53
msgid ""
"This is valid only for distributions *not* having ``fuse3`` installed by "
"default. To be sure, check whether the :code:`fuse3` package is installed, e."
"g., by running :code:`dpkg -l | grep fuse3` in the terminal and checking for "
"a line starting with :code:`ii  fuse3`."
msgstr ""
"此段僅適用於 *未* 預設安裝 ``fuse3`` 的散布版。為確定是否已安裝 :code:"
"`fuse3` 套件，可在終端機執行 :code:`dpkg -l | grep fuse3`，並確認是否有以 :"
"code:`ii  fuse3` 開頭的列。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:55
msgid ""
"If your distribution is using :code:`fuse3`, please refer to the :ref:`next "
"section <ref-ug-troubleshooting-fuse-fuse3>`."
msgstr ""
"若您的散布版使用 :code:`fuse3`，請參閱 :ref:`下一節 <ref-ug-troubleshooting-"
"fuse-fuse3>`。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:57
msgid "Install the required packages::"
msgstr "安裝必要的軟體包::"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:59
msgid "> sudo apt-get install libfuse2"
msgstr "> sudo apt-get install libfuse2"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:62
msgid "In Ubuntu 24.04, the libfuse2 package was renamed to libfuse2t64."
msgstr "在 Ubuntu 24.04 中，libfuse2 套件已更名為 libfuse2t64。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:64
msgid ""
"Now, FUSE should be working. On some older distributions, you will have to "
"run some additional configuration steps:"
msgstr "現在 FUSE 應可運作。在某些較舊的散布版上，您還需要額外設定："

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:66
msgid "Make sure the FUSE kernel module is loaded::"
msgstr "確保已載入 FUSE 核心模組::"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:68
msgid "> sudo modprobe -v fuse"
msgstr "> sudo modprobe -v fuse"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:70
msgid ""
"Then, add the required group (should be created by the install command, if "
"this is the case, this call *will* fail), and add your own user account to "
"this group::"
msgstr ""
"接著新增所需的群組（通常會由安裝命令建立；若已存在，這個指令 *會* 失敗），並"
"將自己的使用者帳號加入該群組::"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:72
msgid ""
"> sudo addgroup fuse\n"
"> sudo adduser $USER fuse"
msgstr ""
"> sudo addgroup fuse\n"
"> sudo adduser $USER fuse"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/notes/user-group-modifications.rst:2
msgid ""
"After adding users to groups, these users must logout and login again for "
"the change to take effect!"
msgstr "將使用者加入群組後，必須登出再登入，變更才會生效！"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:81
msgid ""
"Setting up FUSE 2.x alongside of FUSE 3.x on recent Ubuntu (>=22.04), Debian "
"and their derivatives"
msgstr ""
"在近期的 Ubuntu（>=22.04）、Debian 及其衍生版本上同時設定 FUSE 2.x 與 FUSE 3."
"x"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:85
msgid ""
"This is valid only for very recent (as of April 2022) distributions having :"
"code:`fuse3` installed by default. To be sure, check whether the :code:"
"`fuse3` package is installed, e.g., by running :code:`dpkg -l | grep fuse3` "
"in the terminal and checking for a line starting with :code:`ii  fuse3` (if "
"there is none, your distribution is not using :code:`fuse3`)."
msgstr ""
"此段僅適用於非常新的（截至 2022 年 4 月）且預設安裝 :code:`fuse3` 的散布版。"
"為確定是否已安裝 :code:`fuse3` 套件，可在終端機執行 :code:`dpkg -l | grep "
"fuse3`，並確認是否有以 :code:`ii  fuse3` 開頭的列（若沒有，表示您的散布版未使"
"用 :code:`fuse3`）。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:87
msgid ""
"If your distribution is not using :code:`fuse3`, please refer to the :ref:"
"`previous section <ref-ug-troubleshooting-fuse-fuse2>`."
msgstr ""
"若您的散布版未使用 :code:`fuse3`，請參閱 :ref:`前一節 <ref-ug-"
"troubleshooting-fuse-fuse2>`。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:89
#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:98
msgid "Install the required package::"
msgstr "安裝必要的軟體包::"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:91
msgid "> sudo apt install libfuse2"
msgstr "> sudo apt install libfuse2"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:93
msgid ""
"Now, FUSE 2.x should be working alongside of FUSE 3.x without breaking your "
"system."
msgstr "現在 FUSE 2.x 應可與 FUSE 3.x 同時運作，且不會破壞系統。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:96
msgid "Setting up FUSE 2.x on openSUSE"
msgstr "在 openSUSE 上設定 FUSE 2.x"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:100
msgid "> sudo zypper install fuse libfuse2"
msgstr "> sudo zypper install fuse libfuse2"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:102
msgid "FUSE should now be working."
msgstr "現在 FUSE 應可運作。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:106
msgid "Setting up FUSE on CentOS and RHEL"
msgstr "在 CentOS 與 RHEL 上設定 FUSE"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:109
msgid "The following instructions may be out of date. Contributions welcome!"
msgstr "以下指引可能已過時，歡迎協助更新！"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:111
msgid "Install FUSE from EPEL::"
msgstr "從 EPEL 安裝 FUSE::"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:113
msgid "> yum --enablerepo=epel install fuse-sshfs"
msgstr "> yum --enablerepo=epel install fuse-sshfs"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:115
msgid ""
"Now, add yourself to the related group in order to authorize yourself for "
"using FUSE::"
msgstr "接著把自己加入相關群組，以取得使用 FUSE 的權限::"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:117
msgid "> usermod -a -G fuse $(whoami)"
msgstr "> usermod -a -G fuse $(whoami)"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:123
msgid ""
"If you are on a 64-bit system and want to run 32-bit AppImages (e.g., "
"``x86_64``/``amd64`` to ``i386``, or ``arm64`` to ``armhf``), you will have "
"to install the FUSE runtime libraries for those architectures.::"
msgstr ""
"若您使用 64 位元系統並想執行 32 位元 AppImage（例如從 ``x86_64``/``amd64`` "
"到 ``i386``，或從 ``arm64`` 到 ``armhf``），需要安裝對應架構的 FUSE 執行階段"
"函式庫："

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:125
msgid ""
"> sudo apt-get install libfuse2:i386\n"
"> sudo apt-get install libfuse2:armhf"
msgstr ""
"> sudo apt-get install libfuse2:i386\n"
"> sudo apt-get install libfuse2:armhf"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:130
msgid "Setting up FUSE on Clear Linux OS"
msgstr "在 Clear Linux OS 上設定 FUSE"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:132
msgid ""
"On Clear Linux OS, FUSE *should* be enabled by default. However, if you see "
"the error message mentioned before nevertheless, you can try the following "
"trick:"
msgstr ""
"在 Clear Linux OS 上，FUSE 理應預設啟用。不過若仍看到前述錯誤訊息，可嘗試以下"
"方法："

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:134
msgid ""
"sudo mkdir -p /etc/modules-load.d/\n"
"echo \"fuse\" | sudo tee /etc/modules-load.d/fuse.conf\n"
"sudo reboot"
msgstr ""
"sudo mkdir -p /etc/modules-load.d/\n"
"echo \"fuse\" | sudo tee /etc/modules-load.d/fuse.conf\n"
"sudo reboot"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:142
msgid ""
"This bug was also reported on `reported on GitHub <https://github.com/"
"clearlinux/distribution/issues/273>`__."
msgstr ""
"此錯誤也曾在 `GitHub 上回報 <https://github.com/clearlinux/distribution/"
"issues/273>`__。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:146
msgid ""
"Setting up FUSE on Chromium OS, Chrome OS, Crostini or other derivatives"
msgstr "在 Chromium OS、Chrome OS、Crostini 或其他衍生版本上設定 FUSE"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:148
msgid ""
"FUSE is not operational out of the box. However, starting with release 73, "
"it's fairly easy to install it:"
msgstr "FUSE 預設無法使用。但自第 73 版起，安裝相當容易："

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:150
msgid "sudo apt install fuse"
msgstr "sudo apt install fuse"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:156
msgid "Setting up FUSE on Arch Linux"
msgstr "在 Arch Linux 上設定 FUSE"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:158
msgid "Install the required package:"
msgstr "安裝必要的軟體包："

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:160
msgid "sudo pacman -S fuse2"
msgstr "sudo pacman -S fuse2"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:164
msgid ""
"A common issue, however, is that the ``fusermount`` binary's permissions may "
"be incorrect. Fortunately, there's an easy fix:"
msgstr ""
"不過常見的問題是 ``fusermount`` 執行檔的權限可能不正確。幸好有簡單的修正方"
"式："

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:166
msgid ""
"# bash, dash, bourne shell:\n"
"sudo chmod u+s \"$(which fusermount)\"\n"
"\n"
"# fish shell:\n"
"sudo chmod u+s (which fusermount)"
msgstr ""
"# bash、dash、bourne shell：\n"
"sudo chmod u+s \"$(which fusermount)\"\n"
"\n"
"# fish shell：\n"
"sudo chmod u+s (which fusermount)"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:178
msgid "Fallback (if FUSE can't be made working)"
msgstr "備援方案（若 FUSE 無法運作）"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:180
msgid ""
"If you do not want to (or cannot) set up FUSE, there are fallback solutions. "
"Depending on the AppImage type, you can either mount the AppImage, or "
"extract it and run the contents."
msgstr ""
"若您不想（或無法）設定 FUSE，仍有備援方案。視 AppImage 類型而定，您可以掛載 "
"AppImage，或解壓後執行其內容。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:186
msgid "Extract and run type 2 AppImages"
msgstr "解壓並執行第 2 類 AppImage"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:188
msgid ""
"Most AppImages nowadays are type 2 AppImages. The easiest way to run such an "
"AppImage, if FUSE is not available, is to extract it and then run its "
"contents."
msgstr ""
"目前多數 AppImage 都是第 2 類。若無法使用 FUSE，最簡單的做法是先解壓，再執行"
"其內容。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:191
msgid ""
"Extracting an AppImage to run its contents is pretty expensive. It should "
"only be done if you have no other options left."
msgstr ""
"為了執行內容而解壓 AppImage 的成本較高，只有在沒有其他選擇時才建議這麼做。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:194
msgid ""
"The AppImage runtime has a built-in feature we call \"extract-and-run\". It "
"extracts the AppImage, runs the contents, waits until the app closes, and "
"then cleans up the files again:"
msgstr ""
"AppImage 執行階段內建一項稱為「extract-and-run」的功能。它會解壓 AppImage、執"
"行內容、等待程式關閉，然後再清理檔案："

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:196
msgid ""
"# using a parameter\n"
"./my.AppImage --appimage-extract-and-run [...]\n"
"\n"
"# using an environment variable (which is usually forwarded to AppImage "
"child processes, too)\n"
"# note that this was implemented a while after we introduced the parameter\n"
"# for older AppImages, you might have to use the parameter nevertheless\n"
"export APPIMAGE_EXTRACT_AND_RUN=1\n"
"./my.AppImage [...]\n"
"\n"
"# optionally, you can disable the cleanup if you need to run the AppImage "
"more than once\n"
"export APPIMAGE_EXTRACT_AND_RUN=1\n"
"env NO_CLEANUP=1 ./my.AppImage"
msgstr ""
"# 使用參數\n"
"./my.AppImage --appimage-extract-and-run [...]\n"
"\n"
"# 使用環境變數（通常也會轉傳給 AppImage 子行程）\n"
"# 注意：此功能是在引入參數後一段時間才實作\n"
"# 對較舊的 AppImage，可能仍需使用參數\n"
"export APPIMAGE_EXTRACT_AND_RUN=1\n"
"./my.AppImage [...]\n"
"\n"
"# 如需多次執行 AppImage，可選擇停用清理\n"
"export APPIMAGE_EXTRACT_AND_RUN=1\n"
"env NO_CLEANUP=1 ./my.AppImage"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:211
msgid ""
"In case you have a very old AppImage (i.e., it uses a runtime from the time "
"before \"extract-and-run\" was implemented), you can extract the AppImage "
"manually:"
msgstr ""
"若您使用非常舊的 AppImage（亦即使用了在「extract-and-run」實作之前的執行階"
"段），可手動解壓："

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:213
msgid ""
"./my.AppImage --appimage-extract\n"
"# the contents are extracted into the directory \"squashfs-root\" in the "
"current working directory\n"
"# you can now run the \"AppRun\" entry point\n"
"squashfs-root/AppRun [...]\n"
"# optionally, you can clean up the directory again\n"
"rm -r squashfs-root/"
msgstr ""
"./my.AppImage --appimage-extract\n"
"# 內容會被解壓到目前工作目錄中的 \"squashfs-root\" 資料夾\n"
"# 現在可執行 \"AppRun\" 入口點\n"
"squashfs-root/AppRun [...]\n"
"# 如有需要，可再次清理該資料夾\n"
"rm -r squashfs-root/"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:224
msgid "Mount or extract type 1 AppImages"
msgstr "掛載或解壓第 1 類 AppImage"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:226
msgid ""
"If the process described in the :ref:`previous section <ref-extract-and-run-"
"type-2>` does not work, you likely have a type 1 AppImage."
msgstr ""
"若 :ref:`前一節 <ref-extract-and-run-type-2>` 所述流程無法運作，您可能使用的"
"是第 1 類 AppImage。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:228
msgid ""
"Type 1 AppImages are regular ISO9660 files. They can therefore be *loop-"
"mounted*. Note that you need ``root`` permissions to do so."
msgstr ""
"第 1 類 AppImage 是一般的 ISO9660 檔案，因此可以 *loop 掛載*。請注意，這需要 "
"``root`` 權限。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:230
msgid ""
"sudo mount -o loop my.AppImage /mnt\n"
"# now, you can run the contents\n"
"/mnt/AppRun\n"
"# when you're done, you can unmount the AppImage again\n"
"sudo unmount /mnt"
msgstr ""
"sudo mount -o loop my.AppImage /mnt\n"
"# 現在可執行內容\n"
"/mnt/AppRun\n"
"# 完成後可再次卸載 AppImage\n"
"sudo unmount /mnt"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:238
msgid ""
"You can alternatively extract the AppImage, either using `AppImageExtract "
"<https://github.com/AppImage/AppImageKit/releases/tag/6>`__ or using an "
"extraction tool which supports ISO9660 images (e.g., ``bsdtar``):"
msgstr ""
"您也可以改為解壓 AppImage，使用 `AppImageExtract <https://github.com/"
"AppImage/AppImageKit/releases/tag/6>`__，或使用支援 ISO9660 映像的解壓工具"
"（例如 ``bsdtar``）："

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:240
msgid ""
"# install bsdtar\n"
"sudo apt install libarchive-tools\n"
"# create target directory\n"
"mkdir AppDir\n"
"# extract the contents into the new directory\n"
"cd AppDir\n"
"bsdtar xfp .../my.AppImage\n"
"# now, you can run the entry point\n"
"./AppRun"
msgstr ""
"# 安裝 bsdtar\n"
"sudo apt install libarchive-tools\n"
"# 建立目標目錄\n"
"mkdir AppDir\n"
"# 將內容解壓到新目錄\n"
"cd AppDir\n"
"bsdtar xfp .../my.AppImage\n"
"# 現在可執行入口點\n"
"./AppRun"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:254
msgid "FUSE and Docker"
msgstr "FUSE 與 Docker"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:256
msgid ""
"Most Docker installations do not permit the use FUSE inside containers for "
"security reasons. Instead, you can extract and run AppImages as described in "
"the :ref:`previous section <ref-fuse-fallback>`."
msgstr ""
"多數 Docker 安裝基於安全考量不允許在容器內使用 FUSE。您可以改依 :ref:`前一節 "
"<ref-fuse-fallback>` 所述，解壓並執行 AppImage。"

#: ../../../source/user-guide/troubleshooting/fuse.rst:260
msgid ""
"There's a lot of advice on the internet that follows the scheme, \"just add "
"the arguments ``--cap-add SYS_ADMIN --cap-add MKNOD --device /dev/fuse:mrw`` "
"and it will work\". It is, however, insecure to do so. There's a reason why "
"Docker doesn't support FUSE by default."
msgstr ""
"網路上有很多建議說「只要加上 ``--cap-add SYS_ADMIN --cap-add MKNOD --device /"
"dev/fuse:mrw`` 就能運作」。但這樣做並不安全。Docker 預設不支援 FUSE 是有原因"
"的。"
